    <td align="center" valign="top" height="1" width="137"><a href="Search2.exe?Code=tz6dbsownceptcjp32&dMode=0&KeyWord=&searchMode=1&keyMode=10&fromYear=%97%DF%98a+2%94N&fromDate=%97%DF%98a+2%94N12%8C%8E%92%E8%97%E1%89%EF%81i%91%E63%93%FA12%8C%8E+8%93%FA%81j&tillYear=%97%DF%98a+2%94N&tillDate=%97%DF%98a+2%94N12%8C%8E%92%E8%97%E1%89%EF%81i%91%E63%93%FA12%8C%8E+8%93%FA%81j&speaker=%88%C9%93%A1%95F%91%BE%98Y&speaker1=%88%C9%93%A1%95F%91%BE%98Y&speaker2=&speaker3=&eTarget=1&AhitResult=%8C%9F%8D%F5" target="_top">伊藤　彦太郎</a><br>     
      （勇政）</td>  
    <td height="1" width="500">  
  空き家・空き地対策について<br>
  　１ 市内の所有者不明土地の状況について<br> 
